Caption: Nespelum and barge on Spokane River. From a position just above Camp Spokane, the Nespelum is seen enroute down the Spokane river, pushing the barge on which is delivered men and equipment to clearing operations along the river that are inaccessable (sic) by truck. River bank on right is completely cleared. US WPA 677
